When someone buys a car, a job is added to the job list for a person.
When someone gets paid(every 30 mins?) add a job to the list for a person to deliver that paycheck to their house.
When someone sends mail to another player, add a job to the list for a person.
When someone crashes, allow request of a medic, police or tow truck driver to help.
Allow a player to fix broken things if their job is a repair man.
